- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses different algorithms for solving the discrete logarithm problem and compares their theoretical analysis. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper mentions a prototype implementation of the algorithm. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also relevant as the paper discusses the complexity of the algorithm and compares it to other algorithms in the literature.
